original: Englert, Nils, advokat, Näs:sjö, f. 3/ 11/99 i Röke, Krist. 1. G. 26 m. Signe Åkesson. Barn: Siv f. 28, Stig 37. — Stud:ex. i Lund 19, jur. kand. 27. Förest. f. G. Malmros jur. byrås avd:-kont. i Nässjö 28-30. Egen adv :verks. i Nässjö sed. 30. Led. av Sv:es adv:-tsamf. sed. 34.
translated: Englert, Nils, lawyer, Näs:sjö, b. 3/11/99 in Röke, Kristianstad. Married on 26/married in 1926 to Signe Åkesson. Children: Siv b. 28 and Stig b. 37. Studied at Lund University, graduated in 1919, completed a degree in law in 1927. Worked at G. Malmros' law firm in Nässjö from 1928-1930. Established his own law business in Nässjö in 1930. Member of the Swedish Bar Association since 1934.
